span.span: FWSU serves families, students, and communities in Fairfax, Fletcher, and Georgia, Vermont. Our schools deliver innovative, personalized public education to 1,650 students attending BFA Fairfax, Fletcher Elementary, and Georgia Elementary Middle School. A leader in #VTED, FWSU is proud to be an Apple Distinguished Program and an inductee into the Digital Promise League of Innovative Schools.
